1.1.1.name: wordpress/shootq-integration
1.1.1.description: Integrates your shootQ account with your blog. You can integrate your public contact form into any page or post. You can also integrate your ProPhoto Blog 2, 3 & 4 contact form with shootQ. You can also use Contact Form 7, CformsII and custom forms to send data directly to shootQ. This plugin is provided free by Flaunt Books.
